### Policies - List
GET {{baseUrl}}/policies/?tenant_id=TENANT_01&site_id=SITE_01

### Policies - Create (example payload)
POST {{baseUrl}}/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"_id": "POLICY_01",
	"tenant_id": "TENANT_01",
	"site_id": "SITE_01",
	"anomaly_type": "PPE"
}

### Policies - Get by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/policies/{{policyId}}

### Policies - Update (fill fields to update)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/policies/{{policyId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"_id": "POLICY_01",
	"tenant_id": "TENANT_01",
	"enabled": true
}

### Policies - Delete
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/policies/{{policyId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"_id": "POLICY_01",
	"tenant_id": "TENANT_01"
}

